channel.description:

[code]sendPacket185(15014) Error: T2 - 97,65,81 - 2,3681,2972 - 54,-60,[/code]
I've removed and re-added the interface, so I'm sure it's not me messing up anywhere, it worked on another client I used though...
Any ideas?
